title: Grateful Dead Live at Robert F. Kennedy Stadium on 1992-06-20
description:
Set 1

Cold Rain & Snow, Wang Dang Doodle, Friend Of The Devil, Mexicali Blues-> Maggie's Farm, Row Jimmy, Picasso Moon, Tennessee Jed, Promised Land

Set 2

Corinna-> Crazy Fingers, Playin' In The Band-> Uncle John's Band-> Drums-> Jam-> Casey Jones-> Throwing Stones-> One More Saturday Night*, E:Baba O'Riley*-> E: Tomorrow Never Knows*

*with Steve Miller with Bruce Hornsby on accordion - Steve Miller opened - locomotive airhorn during "Drumz," also to begin "Casey Jones"- "Shenandoah" theme during "Space" - last "Casey Jones": 11-02-84
